articles.author: Daniel Trotta
articles.title: Americans celebrate Thanksgiving on edge over world events - Reuters
articles.description: Americans celebrate Thanksgiving on Thursday with heightened security measures in place and tensions running high over the conflict between Israel and Hamas in Gaza, potentially casting a shadow over a normally joyous holiday.
